{"id": "rios005", "name": "Audio_Academy_495_03_21", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Huff... This is good right? This is the best place in my Academy for getting some sun.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "Watch out! Ball!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Ah!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Catch_Ball", "Catches ball"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "You alright?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Ey? I-I'm fine.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Hey! Can't you see there are people here!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "Sorry, sorry.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Geez...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Um... Thank you...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "No-No need! You're okay, that's all that matters... Eh? In your hand, that's...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "This? It's a calendula. There's not enough sun in my house, so I brought it to the Academy.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">The sorrow of parting.</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Huh?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Oh! I mean that's what the calendula means in the language of flowers, the sorrow of parting. But I believe it also means that good things will soon come your way.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Wah... How'd you know that? That's amazing!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "No, no. It's my brother, he loves useless knowledge like that. Recently, he's been obsessed with the language of flowers. He talks about it every day, so I picked it up without even knowing it.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "So your brother's the amazing one?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Hey! My dad and him always team up on me and call me a dumb meathead. My mom has been nagging me for not learning from him. He was just given a smarter brain...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Sounds like a lively house.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "You mean super noisy!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hahaha... but...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "But what?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I'm kinda jealous... I don't have any siblings and my parents are always busy at work, so they usually aren't around.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "It's okay! I always go to their work and bug 'em! Plus, I'm used to it...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "I can hang out with you...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Er, no... I mean, we can hang out and talk, you know! I don't know much about flowers, not so good at that... But I know a lot about exercising!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Po...POAHAHA!!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Wha-What are you laughing at?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Nothing... Thanks.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Wind", "Gust of wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "The wind's pretty strong... eh? What're you looking at me like that for? Is there something on my face?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "What!? No, I'm looking at the flower, not you!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh, yeah... Ah! It's a little late... I've got to go! We'll talk soon!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Oh... okay, bye.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Ah! Wait! Your name...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Rin! What are you still doing here? Come with me!</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Ah! Okay!</font>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin... your name is Rin...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ふぅ……ここら辺でいいかな？\nアカデミーで一番日が当たる場所だし。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生"], "content": "あぶない！ボールが……！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "きゃっ！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Catch_Ball", "ボールをキャッチする"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "大丈夫か？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え？あ、うん……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">おい！\n人がいんのが見えなかったのかよ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生"], "content": "わりーわりー\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ったく……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あの……ありがとう……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "えっ、いやお礼なんていいって！\nケガがないならそれで……って、それ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "これ？\nキンセンカっていうの。\n家だと日の光に当ててあげられないから、アカデミーに持ってきたんだ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">別れの悲しみ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ああ！悪い悪い。\nキンセンカの花言葉だよ。\n「別れの悲しみ」……\nでも、確か「再び訪れる幸せ」みたいな意味もあったような気がするな。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "へぇ……どうしてそんなこと知ってるの？\nすごい！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "え？い、いやそんなんじゃないって……！\n兄貴！兄貴って変な事に詳しくてさ。\n最近は花言葉にハマってるみたいなんだ。\n毎日毎日聞かされれば、知らない間に覚えちゃうっていうか……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "じゃあ、すごいのはお兄さんだね？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "いやいや、どこが。\n兄貴も親父もいつも俺のこと筋肉バカだって笑うんだぜ？\n母さんまでそれにのって兄貴と違って俺はちゃんと勉強しない～とかグチグチ言ってくるし。\n向こうの方が脳みその出来がいいだけだってのに……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ふふ、楽しそうな家族だね。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "うるさいだけだって！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あはは……でも……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "でも？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "すこし……羨ましいな。\n私、一人っ子だし、お父さんお母さんも仕事人間で、ずっと一人ぼっちだから。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "でもいいの！\n私がベタベタしに行ってるから！\nもう……慣れたし……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "俺がいるよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "へ？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……あ、いや……そういう意味じゃなくて……俺ならいつでもおしゃべりに付き合うし！\n花とかはよく分かんないけど……スポーツに関してなら詳しいぜ！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ぷっ……あはははは！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "なっ！何笑ってんだよ！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "なんでもない……ありがと。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Wind", "風の音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うわ、すごい風……ん？なぁに？\nこっちをじっと見て……私の顔に何かついてる？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "は！？\n花！俺は花を見てたんだよ！\nお前じゃない！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そう？\n……あ！もうこんな時間……私もう行くね！\nまたね！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "あ……おう。\nまたな。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "あ！待って！名前……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凛！\n何してんの！行こ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">え？あ、うん！</font>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛……凛か。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "呼……這裡就行了吧？學院裡最能曬到太陽的地方。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "小心！球！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Catch_Ball", "接球"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？沒、沒事。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">喂！沒看到這裡有人嗎！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "抱歉、抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "真是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那個……謝謝你……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "不、不用道謝啦！沒事就好……咦？妳手上的……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "這個？是金盞花喔。因為家裡曬不到太陽，所以我才拿來學院。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">離別的悲傷。</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "什麼？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "喔！我是在說金盞花的花語，離別的悲傷，不過我記得也有即將到來的幸福的意思。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇……你怎麼知道這些的？好厲害啊！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒、沒有。是我哥啦，特別喜歡冷知識，最近很熱衷花語，他每天講，我就不知不覺記起來了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "所以厲害的應該是哥哥才對囉？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哪有？他常常跟我爸聯合起來嘲笑我只是長了肌肉的笨蛋，我媽也是趁機唸我都不向他學習。他也只是腦袋比較好啦……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你們家感覺好熱鬧哦。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "是很吵才對！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哈哈哈……不過……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "不過？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "有點羨慕……我沒有兄弟姊妹，爸爸媽媽工作比較忙，常常沒辦法陪我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不過沒關係啦！我很常跑去黏著他們！也習慣了……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我可以陪妳啊。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……啊，不是……我的意思是，可以這樣陪妳聊聊！花什麼的知識我不太知道，可能沒辦法……不過聊運動方面的話我很在行的！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "噗……噗哈哈哈！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "妳、妳笑什麼啦！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒有啦……謝謝你。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Wind", "風聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "風好大喔……咦？你怎麼一直盯著我看？我臉上有什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哪有，我是在看花！不是在看妳啦！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "是嗎……啊！有點晚了……我先走了！之後再聊吧！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "喔……好，再見。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "啊！等等！妳的名字……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凜！妳怎麼還在這？一起走吧！</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">欸？好！</font>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜……原來妳叫凜啊……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하아... 여기면 괜찮겠지? 아카데미 내에서도 가장 햇빛이 잘드는 곳이니까.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "앗! 공 조심해!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "앗!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Catch_Ball", "공을 잡는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응? 아, 괘, 괜찮아.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">야! 너희들! 공놀이하려면 사람 있는지 없는지 정도는 확인하라고!</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "아 미안해~ 쏘리~\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "하여간 진짜...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "저기... 고마워...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아, 아니야! 별로 큰일 한 것도 아닌데... 어라? 네 손에...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "이거? 카렌듈라야. 집에는 햇빛이 안 들어서 아카데미로 가지고 왔어.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">이별의 아픔</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아, 그게 카렌듈라의 꽃말이 이별의 아픔이거든... 그런데 다른 뜻도 있는 걸로 기억하는데... 무조건 오게 되어있는 행복.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "와... 그런 건 어떻게 알고 있는 거야? 정말 대단하다!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "벼, 별거 아니야. 우리 형이 잡지식 같은 걸 특히 좋아해서... 최근에는 꽃말에 꽂혔는지 매일 얘기해주거든. 나도 계속 듣다 보니까 나도 모르게 그런 것들을 알게 됐어.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그러니까 대단한 건 네 형이라는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "대단하기는 무슨! 항상 아빠랑 같이 날 놀리려고만 하는 바보 멍청이일 뿐이야! 우리 엄마도 절대 형한테 그런 거 배우지 말라고 하거든. 그냥 골칫덩어리라고 하는 게 더 맞는 표현일 거야...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그래도 가족들끼리 엄청 시끌벅적한가보구나.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그냥 시끄러운 거야!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하하하... 그래도...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그래도?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "조금은 부럽다... 나는 형제도 자매도 없고... 엄마 아빠도 항상 일 때문에 바쁘셔서 보통은 혼자거든.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그래도 괜찮아! 내가 엄마 아빠 있는 쪽으로 자주 가거든! 이젠 익숙해졌어...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "내가 같이 있어줄 수도 있는데.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...아, 그게... 내 뜻은... 지금 이렇게 너의 이야기 상대가 돼줄 수도 있다는 말이야! 꽃에 대해 별로 아는 것이 없어서 꽃과 관련된 이야기를 해줄 수는 없지만... 그래도 운동 쪽은 완전히 꿰고있어!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "푸....푸하하하!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "왜, 왜 웃어!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아니야... 고마워.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Wind", "바람 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "바람이 거세지네... 응? 왜 계속 날 뚫어지게 보고 있어? 얼굴에 뭐