Grass", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "真是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那个……谢谢你……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "不、不用道谢啦！没事就好……咦？妳手上的……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "这个？是金盏花喔。因为家里晒不到太阳，所以我才拿来学院。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">离别的悲伤。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "什么？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "喔！我是在说金盏花的花语，离别的悲伤，不过我记得也有即将到来的幸福的意思。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇……你怎么知道这些的？好厉害啊！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "没、没有。是我哥啦，特别喜欢冷知识，最近很热衷花语，他每天讲，我就不知不觉记起来了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "所以厉害的应该是哥哥才对啰？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哪有？他常常跟我爸联合起来嘲笑我只是长了肌肉的笨蛋，我妈也是趁机念我都不向他学习。他也只是脑袋比较好啦……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你们家感觉好热闹哦。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "是很吵才对！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哈哈哈……不过……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "不过？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "有点羡慕……我没有兄弟姊妹，爸爸妈妈工作比较忙，常常没办法陪我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不过没关系啦！我很常跑去黏着他们！也习惯了……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我可以陪妳啊。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……啊，不是……我的意思是，可以这样陪妳聊聊！花什么的知识我不太知道，可能没办法……不过聊运动方面的话我很在行的！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "噗……噗哈哈哈！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "妳、妳笑什么啦！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "没有啦……谢谢你。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Wind", "风声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "风好大喔……咦？你怎么一直盯着我看？我脸上有什么吗？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哪有，我是在看花！不是在看妳啦！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "是吗……啊！有点晚了……我先走了！之后再聊吧！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "喔……好，再见。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "啊！等等！妳的名字……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凛！妳怎么还在这？一起走吧！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">欸？好！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛……原来妳叫凛啊……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}